    "body": "as title\r\ncc @LeiWang1999 @chengyupku \n\n<!-- This is an auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->\n## Summary by CodeRabbit\n\n* **Refactor**\n  * Softmax max-tracking consolidated across attention kernels: current and previous per-row maxima are merged to improve numerical stability and consistency during attention normalization.\n\n* **Tests**\n  * Transformation tests updated to validate the revised max-tracking behavior.\n\n* **Documentation**\n  * Examples and README updated to describe the new per-row max consolidation step.\n<!-- end of auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->",
